ABOUT YOU AND MY MOTHER.

33:39.506 --> 33:41.174
OH.

33:41.174 --> 33:42.909
WELL,
I SEE YOU KNOW, TOO, HUH?

33:42.909 --> 33:44.578
YEAH, I DO.

33:44.578 --> 33:47.581
SO, AS I SAID,
IF YOU DON'T MIND,

33:47.581 --> 33:49.750
YOUR SISTER ISN'T HERE.

33:49.750 --> 33:52.553
