IS TELL YOUR DAD

34:07.107 --> 34:10.010
NOTHING'S GOING ON
BETWEEN ME AND YOUR MOTHER

34:10.010 --> 34:12.412
AND TO LEAVE
MY PLACE OF BUSINESS ALONE

34:12.412 --> 34:14.681
AND TO GET MY PHONES
BACK ONLINE RIGHT NOW.

34:14.681 --> 34:17.117
OR...

34:17.117 --> 34:19.786
