TO TELL MY DAD THAT I'M GAY.

34:34.968 --> 34:36.436
YEAH.

34:36.436 --> 34:37.470
[ SCOFFS ]

34:37.470 --> 34:40.774
[ SNIFFS ]
OKAY.

34:40.774 --> 34:43.844
SO HE BETTER LEAVE ME
AND MY PLACE OF BUSINESS ALONE.

34:43.844 --> 34:44.778
YOU GOT ME?

34:44.778 --> 34:45.846
YEAH.
OH, YEAH.

34:45.846 --> 34:48.414
I GOT IT.
I'LL ‐‐ I'LL TELL HIM.

34:48.414 --> 34:49.783
GOOD.

34:49.783 --> 34:53.754
‐IS THAT IT?
‐YEAH.

34:53.754 --> 34:55.421
GOOD.

34:55.421 --> 34:58.191
GO ON.
CALL HIM NOW.

34:58.191 --> 35:01.027
NO.
I WILL CALL HIM TOMORROW.

35:01.027 --> 35:03.837
[ CHUCKLES ] LOOK, JEFFERY,
MY SISTER LIKES YOU, ALL RIGHT?

35:03.837 --> 35:05.205
BUT I'LL BUST YOUR ASS
RIGHT HERE.

35:05.205 --> 35:06.540
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

35:06.540 --> 35:09.409
[ CHUCKLES ]
IT'S ‐‐ IT'S HIM CALLING.

35:09.409 --> 35:11.377
AH, YOU SEE HOW THAT WORKS?
ANSWER THE PHONE.

35:11.377 --> 35:12.412
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

35:13.814 --> 35:14.681
HELLO?

35:14.681 --> 35:16.717
‐JEFFERY.
‐Yes?

35:16.717 --> 35:19.720
JUST SAW YOUR MOTHER
IN THE HOSPITAL.

35:19.720 --> 35:21.622
YOU AND I NEED TO TALK.

35:21.622 --> 35:22.656
YEAH, I KNOW.

35:22.656 --> 35:25.325
GO ON.
TELL HIM.

35:25.325 --> 35:26.960
UM, HOW IS SHE?

35:26.960 --> 35:28.562
SHE'S FINE.

35:28.562 --> 35:31.865
WE REALLY NEED TO TALK
ABOUT YOUR RAGE, SON.

35:31.865 --> 35:32.999
IS SHE GONNA BE OKAY?

35:32.999 --> 35:33.867
Yes.

35:33.867 --> 35:36.102
TELL HIM.

35:36.102 --> 35:37.771
WHY DID YOU DO IT?

35:37.771 --> 35:41.007
IT JUST HAPPENED,
RIGHT BEFORE I KNEW IT.

35:41.007 --> 35:44.144
LIKE BOBBY SAFEMAN.

35:44.144 --> 35:45.378
YEAH.
LIKE THAT.

35:45.378 --> 35:48.014
SON, I NEED YOU TO STAY AWAY
FROM YOUR MOTHER.

35:48.014 --> 35:50.083
I KNOW.
I'M ‐‐ I'M TRYING, DAD,

35:50.083 --> 35:51.317
BUT SHE KEEPS COMING AT ME.

35:51.317 --> 35:52.986
WHAT DOES
SHE HAVE ON YOU?

35:52.986 --> 35:55.021
[ SIGHS ]
DAD, I...

35:55.021 --> 35:57.090
Tell me.
I can help you.

35:59.125 --> 36:00.226
NOT ON THIS ONE.

36:00.226 --> 36:04.270
SON, THERE'S NOTHING
YOU CAN'T TELL ME.

36:04.270 --> 36:07.307
TELL HIM.

36:07.307 --> 36:11.745
UM, UH, ACTUALLY, DAD,
I'M STANDING HERE WITH BENNY,

36:11.745 --> 36:14.414
AND, UM, HE'S TELLING ME

36:14.414 --> 36:19.152
THAT, UH, IF YOU DON'T STOP
INTERFERING WITH HIS BUSINESS,

36:19.152 --> 36:21.988
THAT, UH, HE'S GOING
TO TELL YOU THAT I'M GAY.

36:21.988 --> 36:23.990
THE HELL?

36:23.990 --> 36:24.825
What?

36:24.825 --> 36:26.593
IS HE THREATENING YOU?

36:26.593 --> 36:27.427
YEAH.

36:27.427 --> 36:29.462
PUT HIM ON THE PHONE.

36:32.799 --> 36:35.435
HE WANTS ‐‐
HE WANTS TO TALK TO YOU.

36:37.370 --> 36:38.572
YO.

36:38.572 --> 36:41.575
I WILL MEET YOU AT YOUR TOW YARD
IN THREE HOURS.

36:41.575 --> 36:42.576
I'LL BE THERE.

36:42.576 --> 36:44.410
Put my son
back on the phone.

36:46.580 --> 36:49.550
OH, THANKS.

36:53.587 --> 36:54.855
Jeffery, did he harm you?

36:54.855 --> 36:56.056
UH, NO.

36:56.056 --> 36:57.724
DON'T YOU WORRY
ABOUT BENNY YOUNG.

36:57.724 --> 36:58.759
I'LL TAKE CARE OF HIM.

36:58.759 --> 37:00.594
[ SIGHS ]
THANK YOU.

37:00.594 --> 37:02.435
NOW TELL ME
ABOUT YOUR MOTHER.

37:02.435 --> 37:04.971
OH.
DAD, I‐I‐I‐I CAN'T.

37:04.971 --> 37:06.640
OKAY.

37:06.640 --> 37:09.643
OKAY, IN YOUR OWN TIME.

37:09.643 --> 37:11.545
NOW, SON,
YOU KNOW THAT I LOVE YOU.

37:11.545 --> 37:12.912
I KNOW.

37:12.912 --> 37:15.014
THERE'S NOTHING YOU CAN TELL ME
THAT WILL CHANGE THAT,

37:15.014 --> 37:16.983
NOTHING THAT WILL STOP ME
FROM LOVING YOU.

37:16.983 --> 37:18.918
I will move Heaven and Earth
to protect you,

37:18.918 --> 37:21.354
DO WHATEVER I HAVE TO DO
TO PROVE I LOVE YOU.

37:23.123 --> 37:27.260
DAD,
DID SHE KILL MAGGIE DAY?

37:29.462 --> 37:30.463
SON.

37:30.463 --> 37:31.532
DID SHE?

37:36.336 --> 37:38.238
O‐OKAY, OKAY.
LET ME...

37:38.238 --> 37:40.674
LET ME GIVE YOU
AN EASIER QUESTION.

37:40.674 --> 37:44.344
UM, DID YOU SEE WYATT?

37:44.344 --> 37:46.747
YES.
JUST LEFT HIM.

37:46.747 --> 37:49.883
IS IT ‐‐ IS IT TRUE?

37:49.883 --> 37:52.886
YES, I'M ABOUT
TO GO SEE JIM,

37:52.886 --> 37:55.722
GIVE HIM
THE GOOD NEWS.

37:55.722 --> 37:58.859
‐GOOD NEWS?
‐Yeah.

37:58.859 --> 37:59.860
WHAT?

37:59.860 --> 38:01.568
