38:03.637 --> 38:04.805
HE ‐‐ HE WHAT?

38:04.805 --> 38:06.339
OH, SON,
I'M ‐‐ I'M SORRY.

38:06.339 --> 38:07.340
YOU DON'T KNOW.

38:07.340 --> 38:08.609
Wyatt's in the hospital.

38:08.609 --> 38:11.377
I went to the hotel
to I. D. the body.

38:11.377 --> 38:13.479
AND HE'S
IN THE HOSPITAL NOW.

38:13.479 --> 38:14.981
‐REALLY?
‐Yes.

38:14.981 --> 38:17.350
OH.

38:17.350 --> 38:19.820
OH, THAT'S GOOD.
CAN I SEE HIM?

38:19.820 --> 38:21.588
OF COURSE.
I'LL ‐‐ I'LL CALL THE DOCTOR.

38:21.588 --> 38:22.455
THANK YOU.

38:22.455 --> 38:25.058
GO.
GO SEE YOUR FRIEND.

38:25.058 --> 38:26.793
I LOVE YOU, SON.

38:26.793 --> 38:29.062
ALL RIGHT, THANK YOU.
BYE, DAD.

38:29.062 --> 38:30.430
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

38:34.334 --> 38:36.202
Candace: NOT SO CLOSE.

38:36.202 --> 38:38.204
HE DOESN'T KNOW THIS CAR.

38:39.540 --> 38:40.741
IS THAT HIS CAR?

38:40.741 --> 38:42.408
YEAH.

38:43.844 --> 38:47.681
SO HE DOESN'T KNOW
JIM CRYER?

38:47.681 --> 38:48.949
WHAT?

38:48.949 --> 38:52.485
THIS IS JIM CRYER'S
HEADQUARTERS.

38:52.485 --> 38:53.620
SO IT'S JIM CRYER.

38:53.620 --> 38:56.256
YES,
BUT JIM'S IN JAIL, SO...

38:57.558 --> 38:59.192
...WHO WOULD HE
BE HERE MEETING?

39:01.434 --> 39:03.469
WELL, LET'S SEE.

39:03.469 --> 39:05.171
WHAT Y'ALL LADIES DOING?

39:05.171 --> 39:07.641
WHAT THE HELL?

39:07.641 --> 39:09.075
