WITH DAVID HARRINGTON, DOES IT?

39:30.631 --> 39:32.799
WHAT?

39:32.799 --> 39:34.467
COME ON.
YOU KNOW.

39:34.467 --> 39:36.036
KNOW WHAT?

39:36.036 --> 39:37.904
