WITH HIS WIFE.

39:50.050 --> 39:52.352
‐VERONICA, REALLY?
‐YEAH.

39:52.352 --> 39:54.955
YEAH. SO I FIGURED
I'D COME DOWN HERE,

39:54.955 --> 39:56.557
TRY TO SEE
WHAT'S GOING ON.

39:56.557 --> 39:58.859
OKAY.
I DON'T...

39:58.859 --> 40:02.669
